<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BioFarma - Excluir Remédio</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f4f9ff;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #0078d4;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 10%;
        }

        header .logo {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-size: 4em;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: white;
        }

        header nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        header nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .container {
            background: #fff;
            color: #333;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1, h3 {
            color: #0078d4;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #0078d4;
            border: none;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        .btn-danger {
            background-color: #dc3545;
            border: none;
        }

        .btn-danger:hover {
            background-color: #c82333;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .form-control {
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">BioFarma</div>
        <nav>
            <a href="#home">Início</a>
            <a href="#about">Sobre</a>
            <a href="#contact">Contato</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="text-center">Excluir Remédio</h1>

        <h3 class="text-center">Tem certeza de que deseja excluir o remédio <%= @remedio.Remediocol %>?</h3>

        <div class="text-center mt-4">
            <%= button_to 'Excluir Remédio', remedio_path(@remedio), method: :delete, class: 'btn btn-danger' %>
            <%= link_to 'Cancelar', remedios_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
